MysterPage_Tip2: คุณชนะรางวัล
InfoPage1_Scatter: เมื่อกระจาย 9 อันปรากฏบนวงล้อ 2, 3, 4 จะได้รางวัลการหมุนฟรี 7 รอบ
InfoPage1_Stacked_Symbol: สัญลักษณ์ทั้งหมดและวงล้อทั้งหมดจะกองสะสม ยกเว้นสัญลักษณ์กระจาย
InfoPage2_Text1: ระหว่างการหมุนฟรี ตรงกลางของวงล้อ 3 จะกลายเป็นโซนโบนัส ซึ่งจะมีเงินรางวัลกองกลาง 3 กอง หนึ่งกองต่อหนึ่งสัญลักษณ์
InfoPage2_Text2:
เมื่อ
ตกลงไปในโซนโบนัส ท่านจะสามารถรับรางวัลโบนัสสำหรับสัญลักษณ์นั้นๆ
และโบนัสของสัญลักษณ์นั้นจะเพิ่มขึ้น
InfoPage2_Text3:
เมื่อ
ตกลงไปในโซนโบนัส จะได้รางวัลสำหรับสัญลักษณ์ทั้งสามตัว
และรางวัลของสัญลักษณ์ทุกตัวจะเพิ่มขึ้น
InfoPage3_Text1: ปรากฏบนวงล้อ 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, รวบรวมสัญลักษณ์นี้ 3 ตัวขึ้นไปเพื่อเข้าสู่เกมโบนัส
InfoPage3_Text2:
ระหว่างเกทโบนัส จะได้รับลูกแก้ววิเศษ 3 ลูก โดยขึ้นกับรางวัลโบนัสบนลูกบอลเวทมนตร์
มีโอกาสที่ลูลูกแก้ววิเศษจะตกลงไปในที่ว่างใดๆ พร้อมกับโบนัสที่เกี่ยวข้อง
การหมุนแต่ละครั้งจะใช้แถบพลังงานหนึ่งแถบ เกมจะจบลงเมื่อแถบพลังงานถูกใช้หมดสามแถบ
หากคุณได้ลูกแก้ววิเศษ 1 ลูกระหว่างการหมุนใดๆ แถบพลังงานจะถูกเติมเต็ม
เมื่อเกมจบลง จะได้รับรางวัลโบนัสรวมจากลูกแก้ววิเศษ
InfoPage5_Text1:
จะปรากฏบนแกน 1, 2, 3, 4, 5
ทางเลือกแทนสัญลักษณ์อื่นที่ไม่ใช่ SCATTER และ BONUS
StartPage1_Tip1: สัญลักษณ์ตัวคูณไวลด์ที่ปรากฏบนเพลา 2, 3, 4, 5 ระหว่างการหมุนฟรีจะคงอยู่บนเพลาที่ปรากฏออกมา จนกว่าจะจบเกมเล่นฟรี
StartPage2_Tip1: ระหว่างเกมเล่นฟรี จะให้รางวัลการหมุนฟรีเพิ่มเติม 2 ครั้ง สำหรับสัญลักษณ์ตัวคูณไวลด์ 4 ตัวที่ปรากฏออกมา
InfoPage1_Tip1: สัญลักษณ์ตัวคูณไวลด์ที่ปรากฏบนเพลา 2, 3, 4, 5 ระหว่างการหมุนฟรีจะคงอยู่บนเพลาที่ปรากฏออกมา จนกว่าจะจบเกมเล่นฟรี
InfoPage2_Tip1: ระหว่างเกมเล่นฟรี จะให้รางวัลการหมุนฟรีเพิ่มเติม 2 ครั้ง สำหรับสัญลักษณ์ตัวคูณไวลด์ 4 ตัวที่ปรากฏออกมา
InfoPage3_Title1: สัญลักษณ์ไวลด์
InfoPage3_Tip1:
สัญลักษณ์ไวลด์สามารถแทนที่สัญลักษณ์ทั้งหมดได้ ยกเว้นกระจาย
สัญลักษณ์ไวลด์จะปรากฏเฉพาะบนเพลาที่ 2, 3, 4 และ 5 เท่านั้น
ทุกครั้งที่สัญลักษณ์ไวลด์ปรากฏออกมา มันจะถูกสุ่มคูณด้วย x1, x2
หรือ x3 โดยที่ในระหว่างการจ่ายเงินรางวัล
หากมีสัญลักษณ์ไวลด์หนึ่งอันขึ้นไปบนไลน์ที่ชนะรางวัล
วคูณจะถูกคูณระหว่างการจ่ายเงินรางวัล
InfoPage3_Title2: สัญลักษณ์รางวัล
InfoPage3_Tip2:
สัญลักษณ์โบนัส 3 อันขึ้นไปที่ปรากฏบนเพลาใดก็ตาม
จะเริ่มการหมุนฟรี
เมื่อได้สัญลักษณ์โบนัส 3 อันขึ้นไป จะได้รางวัลเดิมพัน 5 เท่า
InfoPage3_Title3: เกมเล่นฟรี
InfoPage3_Tip3:
เมื่อสัญลักษณ์โบนัส 3, 4 หรือ 5 อันปรากฏออกมา
จะได้รับรางวัลการหมุนฟรี 8, 12 หรือ 16 ครั้ง
สัญลักษณ์ไวลด์ที่ปรากฏระหว่างการหมุนฟรีจะคงอยู่บนเพลาที่ปรากฏจนกว่าจะจบเกมเล่นฟรี
เมื่อมีสัญลักษณ์ไวลด์มากกว่า 4, 8 หรือ 10 อัน จะได้รับเกมเล่นฟรีเพิ่มเติมอีก 2 เกม
InfoPage4_Title1: เงินรางวัลสูงสุด
InfoPage4_Tip1:
ไม่ว่าในเกมหลักหรือเกมเล่นฟรี
เมื่อการจ่ายรางวัลสูงถึง
5,000 เท่า มันจะถูกขัดจังหวะและจ่ายรางวัลในทันที
InfoPage4_Title2: ซื้อการหมุนฟรี
InfoPage4_Tip2:
สามารถเริ่มรอบการหมุนฟรีได้ทันทีจากเกมหลักโดยการซื้อด้วยราคา100x
ของเดิมพันรวมปัจจุบัน เมื่อซื้อฟีเจอร์การหมุนฟรี
จะสามารถได้กระจาย 3, 4 หรือ 5
อันแบบสุ่มบนหน้าจอที่เริ่มฟีเจอร์
แล้วจะให้รางวัลการหมุนฟรี 8, 12 หรือ 16 ครั้ง เพย์ไลน์

MysterPage_Tip2: Bạn đã thắng một phần thưởng
InfoPage1_Scatter: 9 SCATTER xuất hiện trên guồng 2, 3, 4, người chơi được trao 7 vòng quay miễn phí.
InfoPage1_Stacked_Symbol: Tất cả biểu tượng và guồng quay được xếp chồng, trừ biểu tượng Scatter.
InfoPage2_Text1: Trong vòng quay miễn phí, phần giữa guồng 3 trở thành Vùng Thưởng. Có 3 tổng giải thưởng - một cho mỗi biểu tượng.
InfoPage2_Text2:
Khi     
rơi vào Vùng Thưởng, bạn có thể thắng phần thưởng tương ứng với biểu tượng
và phần thưởng biểu tượng sẽ tăng lên.
InfoPage2_Text3:
Khi     
rơi vào Vùng Thưởng, tất cả ba biểu tượng sẽ được traon
và tất cả giải thưởng biểu tượng sẽ tăng lên.
InfoPage3_Text1: Xuất hiện trên guồng 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, thu thập 3 biểu tượng trở lên để tham gia ván chơi thưởng
InfoPage3_Text2:
Trong ván chơi thưởng, 3 quả cầu ma thuật sẽ được thưởng tương ứng với phần thưởng trên quả cầu ma thuật.
Có khả năng quả cầu ma thuật sẽ rơi vào bất kỳ vị trí trống nào với tiền thưởng tương ứng của chúng.
Mỗi vòng quay tiêu thụ một thanh năng lượng, trò chơi kết thúc khi ba thanh năng lượng bị xóa.
Miễn bạn nhận được 1 quả cầu ma thuật trong vòng quay bất kỳ, thanh năng lượng sẽ được lấp đầy.
Khi trò chơi kết thúc, tổng thưởng trên quả cầu ma thuật sẽ được trao.
InfoPage5_Text1:
sẽ xuất hiện trên các trục
1, 2, 3, 4, 5Thay thế cho các biểu tượng khác ngoài SCATTER và BONUS
StartPage1_Tip1: Biểu tượng số nhân Wild xuất hiện trên các guồng 2, 3, 4, 5 trong vòng quay miễn phí sẽ ở lại trên các guồng nơi chúng xuất hiện cho đến khi kết thúc ván chơi miễn phí
StartPage2_Tip1: Trong các ván chơi miễn phí, 2 vòng quay miễn phí bổ sung sẽ được trao cho mỗi 4 biểu tượng số nhân Wild xuất hiện
InfoPage1_Tip1: Biểu tượng số nhân Wild xuất hiện trên các guồng 2, 3, 4, 5 trong vòng quay miễn phí sẽ ở lại trên các guồng nơi chúng xuất hiện cho đến khi kết thúc ván chơi miễn phí
InfoPage2_Tip1: Trong các ván chơi miễn phí, 2 vòng quay miễn phí bổ sung sẽ được trao cho mỗi 4 biểu tượng số nhân Wild xuất hiện
InfoPage3_Tip1:
Biểu tượng wild có thể thay thế tất cả các biểu tượng ngoại trừ Scatters;
biểu tượng wild sẽ chỉ xuất hiện trên các guồng thứ 2, 3, 4 và 5
Mỗi khi biểu tượng wild xuất hiện, nó sẽ được nhân ngẫu nhiên với
X1, X2 hoặc X3. Trong trả thưởng, nếu có nhiều hơn một biểu tượng
Wild trên dòng chiến thắng, số nhân sẽ được nhân lên trong
khi trả thưởng
InfoPage3_Tip2:
3 biểu tượng thưởng trở lên xuất hiện trên bất kỳ
guồng quay nào sẽ kích hoạt Vòng quay miễn phí
Khi 3 biểu tượng thưởng trở lên xuất hiện, nhận
gấp 5 lần phần thưởng cược
InfoPage3_Tip3:
Khi 3, 4 hoặc 5 biểu tượng thưởng xuất hiện sẽ được thưởng 8, 12 hoặc 16 vòng
quay miễn phí Biểu tượng Wild xuất hiện trong một vòng quay miễn phí sẽ ở
lại trên các guồng quay nơi chúng xuất hiện cho đến khi kết thúc ván chơi miễn phí
Khi có hơn 4, 8 hoặc 10 biểu tượng Wild, bạn sẽ được tặng thêm 2 ván chơimiễn phí
InfoPage4_Tip1:
Bất kể trong ván chơi thường hoặc ván chơi
miễn phí, khi khoản thanh toán đạt đến 5.000 lần,
nó sẽ bị gián đoạn và thanh toán ngay lập tức
InfoPage4_Tip2:
Vòng CHƠI VÒNG QUAY MIỄN PHÍ có thể được kích hoạtngay lập
tức từ ván chơi chính bằng cách mua nó với 100 x tổng tiền
cược hiện tại. Khi mua tính năng VÒNG QUAY MIỄN PHÍ, 3, 4
hoặc 5 biểu tượng SCATTER có thể quay ngẫu nhiên trên màn
hình kích hoạt và được tặng 8, 12 hoặc 16 vòng quay miễn phí.

QUICK_SPIN_INFO:
通過縮短總旋轉時間
加快遊戲速度
InfoPage1_Scatter: 在2,3,4軸上出現9個scatter將贏得7次免費旋轉次數
InfoPage1_Stacked_Symbol: 除了分散符號外，所有滾輪上的全部符號都會堆疊在一起
InfoPage2_Text1:
在免費轉動期間,在滾軸3的中間位置會變成
獎金區域. 還有3個獎金池- 每種符號各一個
InfoPage2_Text2:
當
落入獎金區域時,
即可贏得符號獎品獎勵且符號獎勵也會增加
InfoPage2_Text3:
當
落入獎金區域時,即可贏得所有三種符號獎品獎勵,所有符號獎勵將會增加
InfoPage3_Text1:
在1,2,3,4,5軸上出現,獲得3個
符號,將可進入獎金遊戲
InfoPage3_Text2:
獎金遊戲中,基本會獲得觸發獎金
遊戲的三顆魔法水珠,以及獲得水
珠上對應的獎金獎勵
會依序在空的位置旋轉看是否獲
得新的魔法水珠及對應獎金
每次旋轉會消耗一個能量條,當三
個能量條清空為結束遊戲
任意旋轉過程中只要有獲得1個魔
法水珠,能量條將會補滿.
遊戲結束時,可獲得所有魔法水珠上
的總獎金
InfoPage5_Text1:
會出現在1,2,3,4,5軸
可替代除了SCATTER及BONUS之外的其他符號
StartPage1_Tip1: 免費旋轉期間出現在轉軸 2、3、4、5 上的百搭乘數符號將保留在它們出現的轉軸上，直到免費遊戲結束
StartPage2_Tip1: 在免費遊戲期間，每出現 4 個百搭乘數符號，將獎勵 2 次額外的免費旋轉
InfoPage1_Tip1: 免費旋轉期間出現在轉軸 2、3、4、5 上的百搭乘數符號將保留在它們出現的轉軸上，直到免費遊戲結束
InfoPage2_Tip1: 在免費遊戲期間，每出現 4 個百搭乘數符號，將獎勵 2 次額外的免費旋轉
InfoPage3_Tip1:
百搭符號可以替代除了獎勵符號以外的所有符號
百搭符號只會出現在第2、3、4及5轉軸
每次百搭符號出現隨機為X1、X2或X3倍率，當支付賠付時該
一中獎線有一個或多個百搭符號，即按其倍率相乘來支付
InfoPage3_Tip2:
獎勵符號出現在任一輪軸上，出現3個以上可觸發免費遊戲
出現3個或更多的獎勵符號，獲得押注5倍獎勵
InfoPage3_Tip3:
出現3、4、5個獎勵符號將獲得8、12、16次免費遊戲
免費遊戲中出現的百搭符號將會停留在出現的輪軸上，直到免費遊戲結束
出現的百搭符號超過4、8、10個以上時，都將額外加贈2次免費遊戲
InfoPage4_Tip1:
不論在基本遊戲或免費遊戲中，
當次賠付達到5000倍時都將立即中斷
InfoPage4_Tip2:
支付100倍注額購買免費遊戲，
購買後觸發轉軸出現3、4或5個獎勵符號，
獲得8、12或16次免費遊戲

InfoPage2_Text1: Selama putaran gratis, bagian tengah dari rol 3 akan menjadi Zona Bonus. Ada 3 total kumpulan hadiah - satu untuk setiap simbol.
InfoPage2_Text2:
Saat
turun ke dalam Zona Bonus, Anda bisa memenangkan bonus yang sesuai
dengan simbolnya dan bonus simbol akan meningkat.
InfoPage2_Text3:
Saat
turun ke dalam Zona Bonus, ketiga simbol ini akan diberi hadiah, dan
semua hadiah simbol akan meningkat.
InfoPage3_Text1: Muncul di rol 1, 2, 3, 4, dan 5, kumpulkan 3 simbol atau lebih untuk memasuki permainan bonus
InfoPage3_Text2:
Selama permainan bonus, 3 bola sihir akan diberi hadiah sesuai dengan hadiah bonus pada bola sihirnya.
Ada peluang bahwa bola sihir akan turun di titik kosong mana pun dengan bonus yang sesuai.
Setiap putaran membutuhkan satu batang energi, permainan akan berakhir ketika tiga batang energi dihabiskan.
Selama Anda mendapatkan 1 bola sihir selama putaran apa pun, batang energi akan tetap terisi.
Ketika permainan berakhir, total bonus pada bola sihir akan diberikan.
InfoPage5_Text1:

StartPage2_Tip1: Selama permainan gratis, 2 putaran gratis tambahan akan diberikan untuk setiap 4 simbol pengali wild yang muncul

InfoPage2_Tip1: Selama permainan gratis, 2 putaran gratis tambahan akan diberikan untuk setiap 4 simbol pengali wild yang muncul
InfoPage3_Tip1:
Simbol wild bisa menggantikan semua simbol kecuali SCATTER;
simbol wild hanya akan muncul di rol ke-2, ke-3, ke-4, dan ke-5
Setiap kali muncul, simbol wild akan dikalikan secara acak dengan X1,
X2, atau X3. Selama pembayaran, jika terdapat satu atau lebih
simbol wild di garis kemenangan, pengali akan
dilipatgandakan selama pembayaran
InfoPage3_Tip2:
3 atau lebih simbol bonus yang muncul di rol
mana saja akan memicu Putaran Gratis
Ketika 3 atau lebih simbol bonus muncul,
dapatkan hadiah sebesar 5 kali taruhan
InfoPage3_Tip3:
Ketika 3, 4, atau 5 simbol bonus muncul, 8, 12, atau 16 putaran
gratis akandiberikan Simbol wild yang muncul selama putaran gratis akan
tetap berada di rol di mana simbol itu muncul hingga akhir permainan gratis
Ketika terdapat lebih dari 4, 8, atau 10 simbol wild, 2 permainan gratis

InfoPage4_Tip1:
Baik di permainan dasar maupun di permainan
gratis, ketika pembayaran mencapai 5.000 kali,
permainan akan berhenti dan segera dibayarkan
InfoPage4_Tip2:
Babak PUTARAN GRATIS bisa dipicu seketika dari
permainan dasar dengan membelinya seharga 100x nilai
total taruhan saat ini. Saat membeli fitur PUTARAN GRATIS,

InfoPage2_Text2:
When

you can win the bonus correspondingto the symboland the symbol bonus will increase.
InfoPage2_Text3:
When

all three symbols will be awarded,and all symbol prizes will increase.
InfoPage3_Text1: Appear on reel 1,2,3,4,5, collect 3 or more symbols to enter bonus game
InfoPage3_Text2:
During bonus game, 3 magic globe will be rewarded corresponding to the bonus rewards on the magic globe.
There's a chance that the magic globe will fall on any empty spot with their corresponding bonuses.
Each spin consumes one energy bar, the game ends when three energy bars are cleared.
As long as you get 1 magic globe during any spin, the energy bar will be filled up.
When game ends, the total bonus on the magic globe will be awarded.
InfoPage5_Text1:

StartPage2_Tip1: During free games, 2 additional free spins will be awarded for every 4 wild multipliers symbols appearances

InfoPage2_Tip1: During free games, 2 additional free spins will be awarded for every 4 wild multipliers symbols appearances
InfoPage3_Tip1:
The wild symbol can replace all symbols except SCATTERl;
the wild symbol will only appear on the 2nd, 3rd, 4th and 5th reels
Every time the wild symbol appears, it is randomly multiplied by X1,
X2 or X3.During payout, if there are one or more wild symbols on the
winning line,  the multiplier will be multiplied during payout
InfoPage3_Tip2:
3 or more bonus symbols appearing on any reel,
will trigger Free Spins
When 3 or more bonus symbols appear,
get 5 times the bet reward
InfoPage3_Tip3:
When 3, 4, or 5 bonus symbols appear, 8, 12,or 16 free spins will be awarded
Wild symbols that appear during a free spin will stay on the reels
where they appear until the end of the free game
When there are more than 4, 8, or 10 wild symbols,
2 additional free games will be given
InfoPage4_Tip1:
No matter in the base game or free game,
when the payout reaches 5000 times,
it will be interrupted and paid immediately
InfoPage4_Tip2:
The FREE SPINS round can be instantly
triggered from the base game by buying it
for 100x the current total bet. When buying the FREE SPINS
feature, 3,4, or 5 SCATTERS can hit randomly on the triggering screen and 8,12, or 16 freespins will be awarded.

InfoPage1_Scatter: 스캐터 9개가 2, 3, 4, 7번 릴에 나타나면 무료 스핀을 보상합니다.
InfoPage1_Stacked_Symbol: 스캐터 심볼을 제외한 모든 심볼 및 모든 릴은 중첩됩니다.
InfoPage2_Text1: 무료 스핀 중에 3번 릴의 중간은 보너스 영역이 됩니다. 3개의 상금 풀이 있습니다. 각 심볼마다 하나씩 있습니다.
InfoPage2_Text2:
보너스 영역에
이(가) 나타나면 심볼에 해당하는 보너스를 획득할 수 있으며 심볼 보너스가 증가합니다.
InfoPage2_Text3:
보너스 영역에
이(가) 나타나면 세 개의 심볼을 모두 보상하고 모든 심볼 상금이 증가합니다.
InfoPage3_Text1:
1, 2, 3, 4, 5번 릴에 나타나면 3개
이상의 심볼을 수집하여 보너스 게임에 입장합니다
InfoPage3_Text2:
보너스 게임 중에 3개의 매직 글로브가 매직 글로브의 보너스 보상에 해당하는 보상을 받습니다.
매직 글로브가 관련 보너스가 있는 빈 곳에 나타날 가능성이 있습니다.
각 스핀은 하나의 에너지 막대를 사용하며 3개의 에너지 막대가 지워질 때 게임이 끝납니다.
스핀 중에 매직 글로브 1개를 받는 한, 에너지 막대가 채워집니다,
게임이 끝나면 매직 글로브의 총 보너스를
보상합니다.
InfoPage5_Text1:
축 1, 2, 3, 4, 5에 나타납니다.
SCATTER 및 BONUS 이외의 기호에 대한 대안
StartPage1_Tip1: 무료 스핀 중에 나타나는 와일드 배수 심볼은 2, 3, 4, 5번 릴에서 유지되며, 무료 게임이 끝날 때까지 해당 위치에 그대로 남습니다
StartPage2_Tip1: 무료 게임 중에, 와일드 배수 심볼 4개가 나타날 때마다 무료 스핀이 두 번 더 주어집니다
InfoPage1_Tip1: 무료 스핀 중에 나타나는 와일드 배수 심볼은 2, 3, 4, 5번 릴에서 유지되며, 무료 게임이 끝날 때까지 해당 위치에 그대로 남습니다
InfoPage2_Tip1: 무료 게임 중에, 와일드 배수 심볼 4개가 나타날 때마다 무료 스핀이 두 번 더 주어집니다
InfoPage3_Tip1:
와일드 심볼은 스캐터를 제외한 모든 심볼을 대체할 수
있으며, 2, 3, 4, 5번째 릴에만 나타납니다
InfoPage3_Tip2:
릴에 보너스 심볼이 3개 이상 나타나면
무료 스핀이 작동됩니다
InfoPage3_Tip3:
3, 4 또는 5개의 보너스 심볼이 나타나면 8, 12 또는 16회의 무료 스핀이 보상됩니다
와일드 심볼이 4, 8 또는 10개 이상일 경우, 무료 게임 2회를 추가로 제공합니다
InfoPage4_Tip1:
기본 게임이나 무료 게임에 관계없이 지급액이 5,000배에
도달하면 즉시 중단되고 즉시 지불됩니다
InfoPage4_Tip2:
무료 스핀 라운드는 현재 총 베팅의 100배에 구매하여
기본 게임에서 즉시 작동할 수 있습니다. 무료 스핀 기능
구매 시 작동 중인 화면에서 3, 4 또는 5개의
스캐터가 무작위로 히트되면 8, 12 또는 16회의 무료 스핀이 보상됩니다.

InfoPage2_Text1:
在免费转动期间,在滚轴3的中间位置会变成

InfoPage3_Text1:
在1,2,3,4,5轴上出现,获得3个
符号,将可进入奖金游戏
InfoPage3_Text2:
奖金游戏中,基本会获得触发奖金

珠上对应的奖金奖励
会依序在空的位置旋转看是否获
得新的魔法水珠及对应奖金
每次旋转会消耗一个能量条,当三
个能量条清空为结束游戏
任意旋转过程中只要有获得1个魔
法水珠,能量条将会补满.
游戏结束时,可获得所有魔法水珠上
的总奖金

一中奖线有一个或多个百搭符号，即按其倍率相乘来支付
InfoPage3_Tip2:
奖励符号出现在任一轮轴上，出现3个以上可触发免费游戏

InfoPage3_Tip3:

The wild symbol can replace all symbols except SCATTERl;
the wild symbol will only appear on the 2nd, 3rd, 4th and 5th reels
Every time the wild symbol appears, it is randomly multiplied by X1,
X2 or X3.During payout, if there are one or more wild symbols on the
winning line,  the multiplier will be multiplied during payout
InfoPage3_Tip2:
3 or more bonus symbols appearing on any reel,
will trigger Free Spins
When 3 or more bonus symbols appear,
get 5 times the bet reward
InfoPage3_Tip3:

where they appear until the end of the free game
When there are more than 4, 8, or 10 wild symbols,
2 additional free games will be given
InfoPage4_Tip1:

when the payout reaches 5000 times,
it will be interrupted and paid immediately
InfoPage4_Tip2:

triggered from the base game by buying it
for 100x the current total bet.

feature, 3,4, or 5 SCATTERS can hit randomly on the triggering screen and 8,12, or 16 freespins will be awarded.
